T02D2935:345a-3: sbyin sreg gi cho ga /'phags pa 'jam dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2935:345a-4: mi g-yo gtum po'i gzugs su snang //
T02D2935:345a-6: rnal 'byor pa la phan bya'i phyir //
T02D2935:345a-7: sbyin sreg rim pa bshad par bya //
T02D2935:345a-8: bkra shis gnas su sa brtag sogs //
T02D2935:345a-9: phyag na rdo rjes byin brlab bya //
T02D2935:345a-10: thab ni zlum po khru gang tshad //
T02D2935:345a-11: dbus su rdo rje sngon pos mtshan //
T02D2935:345a-12: bud shing khru gang yam shing ni //
T02D2935:345a-13: mdzub gang mdog dkar lo 'dab rgyas //
T02D2935:345a-14: dkar gsum la sogs mchod rdzas bsags //
T02D2935:345a-15: dri zhim chu dang me tog bcas //
T02D2935:345a-16: dgang blugs tshad dbyibs rgyu rnams mthun //
T02D2935:345a-17: rgyan la sogs pa dgod byas nas //
T02D2935:345a-18: lha yi rnal 'byor ldan pa yis //
T02D2935:345a-19: me lha bskyed nas mchod pa dang //
T02D2935:345a-20: de rjes thugs ka'i dkyil 'khor mchod //
T02D2935:345a-21: rjes la phyogs skyong mchod par bya //
T02D2935:345a-22: thams cad rtsa sngags nyid kyis mchod //
T02D2935:345a-23: gtor ma'i mgron rnams tshim par bya //
T02D2935:345a-24: bdag gi sbyin sreg rim brtsams pas //
T02D2935:345a-25: las dang nyon mongs dag gyur nas //
T02D2935:345a-26: dam pa'i dam pa nyer thob cing //
T02D2935:345a-27: 'bras bu sku gsum thob par shog / slob dpon
T02D2935:345a-28: chen po bram za bar ma ris mdzad pa 'phags
T02D2935:345a-29: pa rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i sbyin sreg rdzogs
T02D2935:345a-31: / bal po'i pandi ta de ba purna ma ti dang /
